  "texts": [
    "For most clinical-trial datasets, ChatGPT ADA employed a median imputation strategy.",
    "In contrast, it used a zero-imputation strategy for the Hereditary Hearing Loss dataset.",
    "When asked to explain, ChatGPT ADA indicated that its choice was informed by the dataset's inherent characteristics and semantics: \"The data represents the presence (1) or absence (0) of certain genetic variants in patients.",
    "Given this binary representation, median imputation (which would yield either 0 or 1) might introduce bias.",
    "In genetic studies, undetected or missing variants are often interpreted as absent, making zero-imputation align with this understanding\"."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}